item.title: About
item.dc:creator: light-news-fashion
item.content:encoded:
Who are we ?

“Travelling Consultancy Pvt. Ltd. is Nepal based travelling consultancy, registered under private company act of Govt. of Nepal, with quality credentials and trustworthy service guides to reach best possible academic heights based on academic merit and financial capacity. Our primary aim is in assisting competent youngsters to achieve academic heights by anchoring them in exemplary overseas travelling institutions at the right time. We excel in our aim through the convictions and hard work of our staff at the network of our agency. We rightly set the academic goals for aspiring Nepalese prospective students facilitating best travelling opportunities in the prestigious colleges and universities across the world. Committed to the objective of integrity and excellence,  International is an acknowledged agency across Nepal.

Our International relationship?

It is the nature of our business that mandates us to build relation with foreign colleges and Universities to successfully enroll students in a variety of courses and levels. We have a dedicated team which looks after the departments and commits to ensure effective communication and coordination at both ends. As an travelling consultancy, we cannot overlook the merits of international relations as it is one of the attributes that keeps the wheel moving. We have been successful in winning the trust and appreciation of a lot of travelling institutions abroad and will continue to make our presence yet more felt and more visible. In order to fully exploit the new opportunities now available to us worldwide, we have been pursuing a strategy of internationalization based on our firm foundations of promotion student’s mobility from Nepal to a host of countries abroad. We are keen on inking more associations so that we can provide Nepali students with the best of course options and institutions. We have been able to meet the targets set on us by foreign travelling partners and look forward to take the associations to newer heights. We would like to assure all our prospective business associates that we are one of the most prominent names when it comes to abroad studies in Nepal, especially in terms of New Zealand, Australia, USA, Japan and Korea, and we can provide them guaranteed results.

Objective and Mission:

“International with a team of enthusiastic & dedicated professionals with excellent services is determined to meet the requirements of prospective students seeking to study abroad. We are using all the resources available in and outside the country to achieve the goal of providing the better opportunity for Nepalese students. At  International, we understand that each student has different academic and social background as well as his/her truly unique goals for studying overseas. Our objective is to assist them to select the most suitable course and institution based on their personal interests and academic achievement with consummate advice so that they can confidently continue to pursue their travelling goals with achievable success. We value highest possible business ethics and commit to professional standards and integrity, so student can have confidence on our experienced staff that is equipped with updated information available to assist them for identifying student’s travelling paths for further study. Quality service and high standards of business ethics are the foundation of our organization. We are committed to facilitate the students with relevant information about life, travelling, accommodation, post study opportunities, etc accurately. After knowing students’ concerned area of study, we endow them with every minute detail regarding the institution they wish to attend. We support students in every aspect and help them to prepare for the future. We provide minute details on each and every facet of student life abroad. So, we affably request the students interested in abroad study to visit our premises once to feel the difference that how we help you to engrave your future and career.” “Our mission is to make our organization a forerunner in the field of study abroad across Nepal. We believe achieving various milestones in our endeavor and maintain a lead in the market. We are consistent and aggressive to ensure our quality work among Nepalese prospective students.”

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: light-news-fashion
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!
